
> What is JIRA? 
-- It is a work management tool which we can use to manage our projects . track issues, administrative support. 
   It is a product made by ALTASSIAN.

> ALTASSIAN TOOLS - 
-- a> PLAN AND TRACK -> Jira , Jira Align
-- b> SUPPORT  -> Jira Service Management, Statuspage, Opsgenie
-- c> COLLABORATE -> Confluence, Trello
-- d> CODE & BUILD -> Bitbucket , Sourcetree

> JIRA IS USED FOR -
-- Jira is usedto manage business projects for HR, Marketing. 
   It is also used to manage software projects like Agile concepts and features. 

> WHY JIRA?
-- a> It is very popular. 
   b> Everything you need to manage projects and teams will be there. 
   c> It is fully customizable.
   d> Countless apps to further enhance the functionality. 

>  JIRA PLATFORMS ?
-- Two platform deployment types are there - a> Cloud
                                             b> Data Center
   a> Cloud - It is super easy to set up for Cloud. 
              We never have to worry about any maintenance work such as upgrades, security, scalability etc. All of that will be managed and taken care of. 
              It will come with a subscription cost either monthly or annual basis. 

   b> Data Center - It needes to be done by ourselves. 
                    We will be responsible for upgrade, security and performance. 
                    We need to install it by ourselves. 
                    One time installation fee + ongoing support fees will be needed. 
                    As we will be responsible for everything, we can customize things as well. 
                    







